name: HAMILTON CHAMPIONS TM U.S. Dividend Index ETF
longDescription: The investment objective of SMVP is to replicate, to the extent reasonably possible and before the deduction of fees and expenses, the performance of a U.S. equity dividend index. Specifically, SMVP currently seeks to replicate the Solactive United States Dividend Elite Champions Index (or any successor thereto). Fund is designed to track the returns of the Solactive United States Dividend Elite Champions Index, net of fees and expenses. SMVP rebalances quarterly.
